Arrow Capital Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 5:46 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Arrow Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Arrow Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. It primarily provides its services to other pooled investment vehicles. The firm also caters to high net worth individuals and corporations. It manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe. Arrow Capital Management, LLC is based in New York, New York.


499 Park Avenue10th FloorNew York, NY 10022United States



Phone: 212-243-7338

Fax: 212-243-2195

www.arrowcapmgmt.com







